"data/events_special_fleet.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"FLEET_CHAOS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[4]/text"
msgstr "矮人开始阻碍你的通讯信号。你无法与舰队联络。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_fleet.xml.append:297
msgid ""
"data/events_special_fleet.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"FLEET_CHAOS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[5]/text"
msgstr "（伪造ID卡）尝试将你的飞船伪装成叛军船只。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_fleet.xml.append:299
msgid ""
"data/events_special_fleet.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"FLEET_CHAOS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当你递出身份证明时，矮人突然发出尖啸，将你证件上的数据扭曲成一系列认知危害符号。那名叛军成员身体后仰倒下，双眼完全漆黑，口中涌出大量鲜血，其他惊骇的叛军成员立刻进入战斗状态！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_fleet.xml.append:302
msgid ""
"data/events_special_fleet.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"FLEET_CHAOS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[5]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_fleet.xml.append:311
msgid ""
"data/events_special_fleet.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_FLEET_CHAOS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[1]/text"
msgstr "(万斯本尊)\"立正，士兵！我是万斯本尊！退下，并收起你的武器！\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_fleet.xml.append:313
msgid ""
"data/events_special_fleet.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"NEBULA_LIGHT_FLEET_CHAOS\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "万斯正要呼叫舰队，那个矮人突然发出刺耳尖叫企图干扰通讯。将军二话没说一脚把矮人踹到角落，噪音戛然而止。他随即勒令舰队为你们放行。"

